{"tid":663181,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【康城影展】姬蒂白蘭芝撐女權 82位女性電影人齊踏紅毯","createTime":"2018-05-13T05:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T05:40:18.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ab2a10d72f48599fa4ea4b5f1146bb5edeee0ab0","tid":663181,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"金像影后姬蒂白蘭芝（Cate Blanchett）為期12天嘅第71屆康城影展擔任評審主席，而佢剛在當地時間周六就撐參賽電影《Girls of the Sun》，姬蒂白蘭芝帶領來自世界各地嘅女性電影人行紅地毯，總共82人之多，包括女星姬絲頓史釗域（Kristen Stewart）及法國電影新浪潮之母艾麗絲華妲（Agnes Varda）等，呼籲大眾關注歷年少有女性主導電影入圍主競賽之現象，場面相當盛大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180513/large/1526182922_20c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180513%2Flarge%2F1526182922_20c2.jpg&h=d10213e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180513/large/1526182855_71f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180513%2Flarge%2F1526182855_71f8.jpg&h=3585fa62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180513/large/1526182857_2fb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180513%2Flarge%2F1526182857_2fb2.jpg&h=b36a339e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180513/large/1526182858_409c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180513%2Flarge%2F1526182858_409c.jpg&h=a12ef614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180513/large/1526182860_5146.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180513%2Flarge%2F1526182860_5146.jpg&h=4589aea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img